text: Gëzim Dibra (8 November 1956) was a member of the Assembly of the Republic of Albania for the Democratic Party of Albania. Gëzim died on 12 August 2011. He was replaced by Ramiz Çobaj. ==References== Category:Democratic Party of Albania politicians Category:1956 births Category:2011 deaths Category:Place of birth missing Category:Members of the Parliament of Albania Category:21st- century Albanian politicians
